.TH responses
.SH DESCRIPTION
Responses are used by the server to inform clients about required acctions, current state of game module, errors, etc.
.br
The server sends response to the client after each of request made by the client.
.br
Besides that the server can send response to a client any time(not only after client request).
.br
For example an update response or as a resoult of a request from another client that needs confirmation from the owner
of specific module object.
.SH JSON EXAMPLE
.nf
{
  "errors": [
    "Invalid request syntax"
  ]
}
.SH SEE ALSO
responses
